# Vietnamese OCR — Colab Deployment Guide

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Before running, upload the `interface/` folder to your Google Drive at:
> `My Drive/OCR/interface/`

## Drive Structure (Required)

```
My Drive/OCR/
├── checkpoints/final_model/    ← TrOCR model (already there)
├── code/                       ← Existing training/eval code (already there)
│   ├── eval_utils.py
│   ├── address_corrector.py
│   ├── data/
│   │   ├── dataset.py
│   │   └── vietnam_gazetteer.json
│   └── ...
└── interface/                  ← NEW — upload this folder
    ├── app.py
    ├── pipeline.py
    ├── requirements.txt
    └── modules/
        ├── __init__.py
        ├── preprocessor.py
        ├── text_detector.py
        ├── line_segmenter.py
        ├── text_recognizer.py
        └── post_processor.py
```

