## Troubleshooting

| Issue | Fix |
|---|---|
| `ModuleNotFoundError: mmocr` | Run Cell 2 again, or skip — the app falls back to full-image mode |
| `CUDA out of memory` | Reduce batch size in the UI (default 8 → try 4) |
| `eval_utils not found` | Verify `/content/trocr_viet/eval_utils.py` exists |
| `Gazetteer not found` | Verify `/content/trocr_viet/data/vietnam_gazetteer.json` exists |
| `Model not found` | Check the model path points to the correct Drive folder |
